    <p>Up­date your home to make it more flex­i­ble for your cur­rent needs with the com­pre­hen­sive se­lec­tion of home fur­nish­ing so­lu­tions at The Fur­ni­ture</p>
    <p>Mall. With over 35 show­rooms lo­cated un­der one roof, the mall is a con­ve­nient ad­dress to pick up home decor es­sen­tials such as bed­ding, cur­tains and fur­ni­ture. Ten­ants in­clude King</p>
    <p>Koil, The Green Fur­nish­ings and Jasper Home. Till Sept 30, it is run­ning The Great Fur­ni­ture Sale where you can score deals of up to 60 per cent off mall-wide on mat­tresses, din­ing sets, so­fas, car­pets and more.</p>
    <p>The Fur­ni­ture Mall is lo­cated at 10 Toh Guan Road, Sin­ga­pore 608838. Visit www.the­fur­ni­ture­mall.com.sg for more in­for­ma­tion.</p>

